title: Blue Brick Cafe - Dulwich
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, International, Take-out, English
description: All the food is prepared from fresh by Daniel Hughes, life vegetarian and long-time chef. Regularly changing menu. Some examples include borscht soup, hummus and baba ganoush with pita, roast squash salad with sprouts and walnuts, vegetable curry with organic rice, spaghetti with oven roast tomatoes, veggie sausages with mash and red wine gravy. Vegan breakfast options  include smoothies, chocolate pudding with rhubarb and ginger. Also serves organic baby food. Phone ahead if you have a group of people.
